Test-case softwarecenter/install-app
<dl>
    <dt>Open the Software Center</dt>
    <dt>Search and select any graphical application that has not been yet installed</dt>
    <dt>Press Install to install the application</dt>
        <dd>A standard authentication dialog should pop out</dd>
        <dd>The icon for the installing application should appear on the Launcher</dd>
        <dd>After hovering the mouse pointer over the installing application icon on the Launcher a "Waiting to install" tooltip should appear</dd>
    <dt>Proceed with the installation process</dt>
        <dd>After installing the application, its icon should be visible on the Launcher</dd>
</dl>
Test-case softwarecenter/uninstall-app
<dl>
    <dt>Open the Software Center</dt>
    <dt>Search and install any graphical application</dt>
        <dd>Its icon should be added to the Launcher</dd>
    <dt>Using Software Center uninstall the newly installed application</dt>
        <dd>The uninstalled application icon should disappear from the Launcher</dd>
</dl>
<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'failed' result and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result.</strong>
